  "privacyPolicyTitle": "Privacy Policy",
  "privacyPolicyLastUpdated": "Last updated: May 13, 2026",
  "privacySection1Title": "1. General Provisions",
  "privacySection1Body": "The AI Stain Fix application (hereinafter referred to as the \"Application\") is designed to help users remove stains from various types of fabrics. This Privacy Policy describes what data we collect, how we use it, and how we protect it.",
  "privacySection2Title": "2. Data We Collect",
  "privacySection2Body": "• Stain photos — used exclusively for analyzing the type of contamination and generating removal instructions.\n\n• Technical device information — OS version, device model, interface language (to improve service quality).\n\n• Purchase data — information about acquired packages and subscriptions (processed by the RuStore payment system).",
  "privacySection3Title": "3. Photo Processing",
  "privacySection3Body": "Photos are transmitted to a secure server for image analysis and instruction generation.\n\nPhotos are not stored on the server after processing and are not shared with third parties. Images are used exclusively for generating stain removal recommendations.",
  "privacySection4Title": "4. Data Storage",
  "privacySection4Body": "Analysis history is stored locally on your device. We do not have access to your local history.\n\nThe proxy server does not keep request logs and does not store uploaded images.",
  "privacySection5Title": "5. Security",
  "privacySection5Body": "All data is transmitted via the secure HTTPS protocol. We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access.",
  "privacySection6Title": "6. User Rights",
  "privacySection6Body": "You can at any time:\n• Delete analysis history on your device\n• Delete the application and all associated data\n• Contact us with questions about your data",
  "privacySection7Title": "7. Contact",
  "privacySection7Body": "For privacy inquiries, contact:\nai.stain.fix.app@gmail.com",
  "termsTitle": "Terms of Service",
  "termsLastUpdated": "Last updated: May 13, 2026",
  "termsSection1Title": "1. Subject of Agreement",
  "termsSection1Body": "This Terms of Service agreement (hereinafter referred to as the \"Agreement\") governs the relationship between the developer of the AI Stain Fix application (hereinafter referred to as the \"Developer\") and the user (hereinafter referred to as the \"User\"), arising from the use of the AI Stain Fix mobile application (hereinafter referred to as the \"Application\").",
  "termsSection2Title": "2. Service Description",
  "termsSection2Body": "The Application provides a service for analyzing photos of stains using image recognition technologies and generating removal recommendations. Recommendations are for informational purposes only.",
  "termsSection3Title": "3. Terms of Use",
  "termsSection3Body": "• The User agrees to use the Application only for lawful purposes.\n\n• The free plan includes 3 analyses per day.\n\n• Additional analyses are available through purchasing packages or subscribing to PRO.\n\n• The User is responsible for the quality of provided photos.",
  "termsSection4Title": "4. Limitation of Liability",
  "termsSection4Body": "Recommendations provided by the Application are for informational purposes only. The Developer is not responsible for:\n\n• Damage to fabric or items when following recommendations\n• Allergic reactions to recommended products\n• Inaccuracy in determining the type of stain or fabric\n• Service interruptions due to technical reasons\n\nBefore applying any product, it is recommended to test it on an inconspicuous area of the fabric.",
  "termsSection5Title": "5. Paid Services",
  "termsSection5Body": "Payment is processed through the RuStore payment system. Refund conditions are determined by RuStore rules.\n\nPRO subscription renews automatically unless canceled 24 hours before the end of the current period.",
  "termsSection6Title": "6. Intellectual Property",
  "termsSection6Body": "All rights to the Application, its design, code, and content belong to the Developer. The User is granted a non-exclusive license to use the Application for personal non-commercial purposes.",
  "termsSection7Title": "7. Changes to Terms",
  "termsSection7Body": "The Developer reserves the right to change the terms of this Agreement. The current version is always available in the \"Settings\" section of the Application.",
  "termsSection8Title": "8. Contact",
  "termsSection8Body": "For questions related to this Agreement:\nai.stain.fix.app@gmail.com"
